- âš–ï¸ **Compliance-Ready** â€” JSON logs for GDPR, HIPAA, and internal audits  
- ğŸ› **Debugging Superpower** â€” Trace errors to exact rows and steps  
- ğŸ”§ **Simple Integration** â€” One decorator audits any function (lists, dicts, CSVs)

